CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1952, pg. 20, reads: "Getting Letters At Fifth - Fifth Avenue High School's athletes were presented their letters at a banquet held in school cafeteria at noon on Tuesday. Among those receiving the letters from Dr. Ralph Scott (far left) were Paul Tomasonich and Jewel Letbetter, who is a three-letter man. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Fifth Avenue High School Principal Ralph Scott presenting letters to athletes Paul Tomasonich or Domastovich and Jewel or Jewell Ledbetter during banquet in Fifth Avenue High School cafeteria
